                "invention-title": [
                    "Carbon oxide absorbent, absorption method and application",
                    "碳氧化物吸收剂、吸收方法及应用"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses an oxycarbide absorbent, an absorption method and application. The oxycarbide absorbent comprises calcium oxide and sodium hydroxide. According to the method, the proper oxycarbide absorbent is selected, CO and CO2 can be fixed in carbonate at the same time through the oxycarbide absorbent at the low temperature, CO and sodium hydroxide can also react to generate hydrogen, preparation and collection of high-purity hydrogen can be achieved when the method is applied to biomass alkali heat hydrogen production, and the method is suitable for industrial production. The problem that the purity of hydrogen is influenced by carbon oxides in a conventional two-stage process is solved, and a high-quality hydrogen product is obtained."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了碳氧化物吸收剂、吸收方法及应用，碳氧化物吸收剂包括氧化钙和氢氧化钠。本申请中选择合适的碳氧化物吸收剂，在较低温度下碳氧化物吸收剂就能够将CO、CO2同时固定在碳酸盐中，且CO与氢氧化钠反应也可以生成氢气，应用在生物质碱热制氢中可以实现高纯氢气的制备和收集，克服了常规两段式工艺中碳氧化合物影响氢气纯度的问题，获得了高品质的氢气产品。"
                }
            ]
